I've been going to Estetica Beauty for my facial appointments for many years. The staff are very considerate when dealing with their customers, making sure their customers are always comfortable.
They also advise customers on the different packages that suit the customers' budget and preferences.
The rooms are also relaxing to be in, with a relaxing atmosphere that allows you to unwind.
Additionally, they are also flexible with their slots and scheduling, making it a hassle free experience.
Strongly recommend to go.
